<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q27_v4" title="Q27 Variante 4" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float"><qti-default-value><qti-value>0</qti-value></qti-default-value></qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>
      Para bordear un tapete rectangular, se dispone de 
      <m:math>
        <m:mrow>
          <m:mo>(</m:mo>
          <m:mn>34</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
          <m:mo>+</m:mo>
          <m:mn>26</m:mn>
          <m:mo>)</m:mo>
        </m:mrow>
      </m:math>
      metros de cinta. Cada lado largo mide 
      <m:math>
        <m:mrow>
          <m:mo>(</m:mo>
          <m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
          <m:mo>+</m:mo>
          <m:mn>5</m:mn>
          <m:mo>)</m:mo>
        </m:mrow>
      </m:math>
      metros y cada lado corto mide 
      <m:math>
        <m:mrow>
          <m:mo>(</m:mo>
          <m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
          <m:mo>−</m:mo>
          <m:mn>2</m:mn>
          <m:mo>)</m:mo>
        </m:mrow>
      </m:math>
      metros.
      La cantidad de cinta sobrante, en metros, se modela mediante la expresión:
      
      <m:math>
        <m:mrow>
          <m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo>
          <m:mo>(</m:mo>
          <m:mn>34</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
          <m:mo>+</m:mo>
          <m:mn>26</m:mn>
          <m:mo>)</m:mo>
          <m:mo>−</m:mo>
          <m:mo>[</m:mo>
          <m:mo>(</m:mo>
          <m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
          <m:mo>+</m:mo>
          <m:mn>5</m:mn>
          <m:mo>)</m:mo>
          <m:mo>+</m:mo>
          <m:mo>(</m:mo>
          <m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
          <m:mo>+</m:mo>
          <m:mn>5</m:mn>
          <m:mo>)</m:mo>
          <m:mo>+</m:mo>
          <m:mo>(</m:mo>
          <m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
          <m:mo>−</m:mo>
          <m:mn>2</m:mn>
          <m:mo>)</m:mo>
          <m:mo>+</m:mo>
          <m:mo>(</m:mo>
          <m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
          <m:mo>−</m:mo>
          <m:mn>2</m:mn>
          <m:mo>)</m:mo>
          <m:mo>]</m:mo>
        </m:mrow>
      </m:math>
      
      Antes de simplificar completamente, se pueden reagrupar los términos semejantes dentro del corchete.
      
      ¿Cuál de las siguientes expresiones corresponde a una reagrupación algebraicamente coherente de la expresión anterior?
    </p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      <qti-prompt>Elige la opción que muestra una reagrupación correcta de los términos semejantes.</qti-prompt>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo>
            <m:mn>34</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>26</m:mn>
            <m:mo>)</m:mo>
            <m:mo>−</m:mo>
            <m:mo>[</m:mo>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo>
            <m:mn>18</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>16</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
            <m:mo>)</m:mo>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo>
            <m:mn>10</m:mn>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>4</m:mn>
            <m:mo>)</m:mo>
            <m:mo>]</m:mo>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Al reagrupar dentro del corchete, los términos con x sí dan 18x + 16x, pero los términos independientes son 5 + 5 − 2 − 2 = 10 − 4, no 10 + 4. Por eso esta expresión no es algebraicamente coherente con la original.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo>
            <m:mn>34</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>26</m:mn>
            <m:mo>)</m:mo>
            <m:mo>−</m:mo>
            <m:mo>[</m:mo>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo>
            <m:mn>18</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>16</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
            <m:mo>)</m:mo>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo>
            <m:mn>10</m:mn>
            <m:mo>−</m:mo>
            <m:mn>4</m:mn>
            <m:mo>)</m:mo>
            <m:mo>]</m:mo>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Dentro del corchete, los dos lados largos aportan 9x + 9x = 18x y 5 + 5 = 10; los dos lados cortos aportan 8x + 8x = 16x y −2 − 2 = −4. Por eso una reagrupación coherente es (18x + 16x) + (10 − 4).</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo>
            <m:mn>34</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>26</m:mn>
            <m:mo>)</m:mo>
            <m:mo>−</m:mo>
            <m:mo>[</m:mo>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo>
            <m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
            <m:mo>)</m:mo>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo>
            <m:mn>5</m:mn>
            <m:mo>−</m:mo>
            <m:mn>2</m:mn>
            <m:mo>)</m:mo>
            <m:mo>]</m:mo>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. En el corchete aparecen dos veces (9x + 5) y dos veces (8x − 2). Por eso la reagrupación debe considerar 9x + 9x = 18x, 8x + 8x = 16x, 5 + 5 = 10 y −2 − 2 = −4. Esta opción solo muestra una vez cada término y no representa toda la suma original.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo>
            <m:mn>34</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>26</m:mn>
            <m:mo>)</m:mo>
            <m:mo>−</m:mo>
            <m:mo>[</m:mo>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo>
            <m:mn>18</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
            <m:mo>)</m:mo>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo>
            <m:mn>10</m:mn>
            <m:mo>−</m:mo>
            <m:mn>2</m:mn>
            <m:mo>)</m:mo>
            <m:mo>]</m:mo>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Los términos repetidos deben sumarse dos veces: 8x + 8x = 16x, no 8x, y −2 − 2 = −4, no −2. Por eso la reagrupación correcta dentro del corchete no puede ser (18x + 8x) + (10 − 2).</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Observar la expresión dentro del corchete</strong></p>
            <p>La expresión interior es:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mo>(</m:mo>
                <m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
                <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                <m:mn>5</m:mn>
                <m:mo>)</m:mo>
                <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                <m:mo>(</m:mo>
                <m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
                <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                <m:mn>5</m:mn>
                <m:mo>)</m:mo>
                <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                <m:mo>(</m:mo>
                <m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
                <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                <m:mo>)</m:mo>
                <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                <m:mo>(</m:mo>
                <m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
                <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                <m:mo>)</m:mo>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Reagrupar los términos con variable</strong></p>
            <p>Los términos con <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math> son:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
                <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                <m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
                <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                <m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
                <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                <m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mn>18</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
                <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                <m:mn>16</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Reagrupar los términos independientes</strong></p>
            <p>Los términos numéricos son:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mn>5</m:mn>
                <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                <m:mn>5</m:mn>
                <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mn>10</m:mn>
                <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                <m:mn>4</m:mn>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Escribir la reagrupación dentro del corchete</strong></p>
            <p>Entonces, antes de simplificar completamente, el corchete puede escribirse como:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mo>[</m:mo>
                <m:mo>(</m:mo>
                <m:mn>18</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
                <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                <m:mn>16</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi>
                <m:mo>)</m:mo>
                <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                <m:mo>(</m:mo>
                <m:mn>10</m:mn>
                <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                <m:mn>4</m:mn>
                <m:mo>)</m:mo>
                <m:mo>]</m:mo>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La expresión algebraicamente coherente es la <strong>opción B</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>